    ⚡ QUICK INSTALLATION:
    ──────────────────────────────────────────────────
    [1] DOWNLOAD    →  JetBrains_All_Products.rar
    [2] EXTRACT     →  WinRAR or 7-Zip
    [3] RUN         →  Toolbox_Installer.exe (as administrator)
    [4] INSTALL     →  JetBrains Toolbox App
    [5] SELECT      →  Desired IDEs from the toolbox
    [6] ACTIVATE    →  With your license key or account
    ──────────────────────────────────────────────────

    ⚡ HOW THE PROGRAM WORKS:
    ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
    
    🔹 THE TOOLBOX APP — CENTRAL MANAGEMENT
    The JetBrains Toolbox App serves as the central hub for managing all your JetBrains tools . It provides:
    
    • One-click installation of any JetBrains IDE
    • Automatic updates for all installed products
    • Version management (install multiple versions side-by-side)
    • Quick project access from anywhere
    • Settings synchronization across different machines
    • Centralized licensing management
    
    🔹 PRODUCTS INCLUDED
    The All Products Pack includes the complete lineup of JetBrains professional tools :
    
    🟢 INTELLIJ IDEA ULTIMATE
    The most intelligent Java IDE with advanced refactorings, on-the-fly code assistance, profound navigation, smart completion, and blazing performance. Supports Java, Kotlin, Scala, Groovy, and all JVM languages with enterprise framework integrations .
    
    🟢 PYCHARM PROFESSIONAL
    Complete Python IDE with support for web development using Django, Flask, and Google App Engine. Includes scientific tools for data science with matplotlib, NumPy, and Anaconda integration .
    
    🟢 WEBSTORM
    Lightweight IDE for professional JavaScript and front-end development. Supports Angular, React, Vue.js, and Node.js with intelligent coding assistance .
    
    🟢 CLION
    Cross-platform C/C++ IDE with CMake integration, code analysis, and powerful debugger. Perfect for embedded, systems, and performance-critical development .
    
    🟢 RIDER
    Cross-platform .NET IDE for ASP.NET, .NET Core, Xamarin, and Unity game development. Combines IntelliJ platform features with ReSharper's powerful .NET capabilities .
    
    🟢 PHPSTORM
    Professional PHP IDE with support for Symfony, Laravel, Drupal, WordPress, and all major PHP frameworks. Includes database tools and JavaScript support .
    
    🟢 RUBYMINE
    Ruby and Rails IDE with intelligent coding assistance, refactorings, and debugging tools for Ruby development .
    
    🟢 DATAGRIP
    Multi-engine database IDE for SQL Server, Oracle, PostgreSQL, MySQL, and more. Delivers an intelligent SQL editor and database tools .
    
    🟢 GOLAND
    Powerful Go language IDE with advanced coding assistance, refactoring, and debugging tools specifically designed for Go developers .
    
    🟢 RIDER
    Complete IDE for game developers using Unity, with deep integration and C# support .
    
    🟢 RUSTROVER
    Dedicated Rust IDE with code completion, debugging, and Cargo integration .
    
    🟢 DATA SPELL
    Data science IDE with Jupyter notebook support, interactive Python, and R language integration .
    
    🔹 ADDITIONAL TOOLS 
    
    • RE SHARPER: Visual Studio extension for .NET developers with code inspections, refactorings, and navigation
    • RE SHARPER C++: C++ productivity tool for Visual Studio
    • DOT COVER: .NET unit test runner and code coverage tool
    • DOT MEMORY: .NET memory profiler
    • DOT TRACE: .NET performance profiler
    • CODE WITH ME: Collaborative development and pair programming tool
    
    🔹 CORE FUNCTIONALITY
    All JetBrains IDEs share a common platform with these powerful features :
    
    • INTELLIGENT CODE COMPLETION: Context-aware suggestions that understand your codebase
    • REAL-TIME ERROR DETECTION: Instant feedback on syntax errors, typos, and potential bugs
    • ADVANCED REFACTORING: Automated code transformations with safety checks
    • POWERFUL NAVIGATION: Jump to definitions, usages, and implementations instantly
    • BUILT-IN VERSION CONTROL: Seamless Git, SVN, and Mercurial integration
    • DEBUGGING TOOLS: Multi-language debugging with breakpoints, watches, and evaluation 
    • TESTING FRAMEWORKS: Integrated unit testing with popular frameworks
    • DATABASE TOOLS: SQL execution, schema management, and data editing
    • TERMINAL: Integrated command line for your workflow
    • TASK MANAGEMENT: Connect to Jira, YouTrack, and other issue trackers
    
    🔹 AI ASSISTANT INTEGRATION
    The All Products Pack now includes AI Pro features for enhanced productivity :
    
    • JUNIE CODING AGENT: AI pair programmer that can answer questions, propose plans, and follow development guidelines
    • AI CODE COMPLETION: Unlimited intelligent code suggestions
    • LOCAL AI MODELS: Privacy-focused AI processing on your machine
    • CLOUD MODEL ACCESS: Optional integration with Claude 3.7, Google Gemini, and OpenAI
    • CONTEXT-AWARE SUGGESTIONS: AI that understands your entire project structure
    
    🔹 LICENSE ACTIVATION METHODS 
    The pack can be activated in multiple ways:
    
    • JETBRAINS ACCOUNT: Login with your account for automatic activation
    • LICENSE SERVER: Connect to organizational license server
    • ACTIVATION CODE: Enter a standalone license key
    • FLOATING LICENSES: For organizations sharing licenses across teams 
    
    🔹 CROSS-PLATFORM SUPPORT 
    All tools run identically on:
    
    • WINDOWS: 10/11 (64-bit)
    • MACOS: Intel and Apple Silicon
    • LINUX: Major distributions with desktop environments
    
    🔹 TEAM COLLABORATION TOOLS
    Additional team productivity tools included :
    
    • TEAMCITY: Continuous integration and build management
    • YOU TRACK: Keyboard-centric bug and issue tracker
    • UPSOURCE: Code repository browser and review tool
    • HUB: Centralized user management and project dashboard
    ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

    ⚡ SYSTEM REQUIREMENTS:
    ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
    OS              │ Windows 10/11, macOS (Intel/Apple Silicon), Linux
    RAM             │ 4GB minimum (8GB+ recommended) 
    Storage         │ 1.5GB per IDE + 1GB for caches 
    Screen          │ 1024×768 minimum, 1920×1080 recommended 
    JDK             │ Bundled with each IDE (no separate installation needed)
    .NET            │ For Rider and .NET tools: .NET 6.0+ recommended
